e":"Hadith on Salat: What to say when Imam rises in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the Imam says, \u2018Allah heard those who praise him,\u2019 then say, \u2018Our Lord, for you is praise.\u2019 If one\u2019s statement coincides with the statement of the angels, his previous sins will be forgiven.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12013,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/04\/repeat-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":25173,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Repeat what is said by the caller to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you hear the call to prayer, say something similar to what the caller has said.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 611, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 383 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33170,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/what-imam-says-in-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":25173,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: What the Imam and followers say in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah heard those who praise him,\u201d he would say, \u201cO Allah, our Lord, for you is praise.\u201d When the Prophet bowed and raised his head, he would declare the greatness of Allah. When he stood from the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/believer-or-merely-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":25173,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Or maybe he is merely a Muslim?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity, so I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, give it to this man for he is a believer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOr merely a Muslim.\u201d I said it three times and the Prophet repeated it three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3231,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/19\/intended-to-kill-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":25173,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Two Muslims fighting are both in Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf two Muslims confront each other with swords, both the killer and the killed will be in Hellfire.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, we understand for the killer, but why for the one killed?\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25173","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25173"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25173\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25173"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=25173"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=25173"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}